{"title":"煤忆","authors":["韩青"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":2,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤忆（外一章）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕生的追求，终于在一朝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升华。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你公开久蓄的秘密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"释放无畏的赤诚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃亮大千世界的光明之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不错，你是黑暗的叛逆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了迎候光明的降临，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你才有如此超凡的耐性。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜因之而光辉灿烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严寒因之而温馨如春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧还你以夙愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧完成轰轰烈烈的再"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜航，在默默地行进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿井口是启航的码头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巷道是行驶的航线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿灯是向导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮夜之旅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月黑夜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真诚的夜航者在默默地行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心是飞渡之舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜漫漫兮与之交通、神游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淡远了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那花卉的幽香，鸟语的闲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"适，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及外面世界的声声色色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已如飘逝的岁月之波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而伴之探索夜航的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有人生的主题："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作着是神圣的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰仗着这信念的指南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不会迷向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不会半途而废，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就能超越自我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作着是神圣的——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨越重重艰辛和惊险之后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就采摘到了光明的火种……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是神话故事的重复，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是精诚所至必然的收获。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}